updates.HtmlString: Added in tokens which were completely missing. Updated marketing cards to be more accurate for set, plus set chances as 1:3 token:marketing for core sets, 2:3 for expansions, and 9:1 as of Battle for Zendikar.
Updated foil chances. Now 15/67 chance a booster has a foil and includes basic lands.
Now includes prelrease promos. Thanks Madigan!
Will no longer include duplicates in seeded booster.
Now includes a guildgate in the last slot of each guild seeded booster.
